# =============================================================================
#  BOF — public repo hygiene
#
#  This is a PUBLIC repo (github.com/dcmjlt/bof-web). Only the deployable
#  static site + deploy config is tracked. Everything strategic, internal,
#  or working stays local-only.
#
#  Tracked (intentionally): index.html, privacy.html, robots.txt,
#  sitemap.xml, netlify.toml, netlify/functions/**, README.md, .gitignore
# =============================================================================

# --- OS / editor noise ---
.DS_Store
*.swp

# --- Local tooling / agent state (not part of the published site) ---
.gstack/
.claude/
.agents/
skills-lock.json

# --- Internal strategy & working documents (NEVER publish) ---
CLAUDE.md
AGENTS.md
POSITIONING.md
DESIGN.md
product.md
TODOS.md
copywriting-guide*.md
SEO-suggestion-homepage.md
SEO-*.md

# --- Internal source material (pitch / branding / sitemap / USP) ---
*.pdf

# --- Designer share material & logo sources (working assets) ---
mockup-share/

# --- Print / stand assets (generated working artefacts) ---
print/
